name: The Pastel Taguara
description:
On the shores of the universe "La Tokenia" there is a small place called "The Pastel Taguara" a corner that welcomes the visitors with the warmth of the sun, the smell of the sea and a Polarcita beer *"vestida de novia" in the hand.
(*Dressed as a bride: The way a beer is called when the bottle looks frosted.)
